                  <p>At The Address, when we say creativity, we mean creativity with relevance. Our production
                     department has modern technologies and expertise to handle all forms of artworks and
                     videos in the traditional media, new media and anything in-between. We do</p>
                  <ul>
                     <li>Animation</li>
                     <li>Graphic designing</li>
                     <li>Responsive websites</li>
                     <li>Video(s)-for-marketing services</li>
                     <li>TV, press, radio and online copywriting and production</li>
                     <li>Production of marketing collaterals – banners, fliers, brochures, cards etc</li>
                  </ul>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="col-12 d-flex align-self-stretch ftco-animate">
